---
description: Visual system rules for Academy Realtors.
globs:
  - src/styles/**/*
  - src/components/**/*
  - src/app/**/*
---

Keep the visual system stable:
- Use shared tokens instead of ad-hoc values.
- Keep container widths and spacing scales consistent.
- Reuse primitives before creating new UI variants.
- Avoid random colors, radii, shadows, and motion.
- Keep layout, component, and product surfaces on the same semantic token set.
- Make page composition feel deliberate and restrained.
